Analytical Ability

Demonstrates strong analytical ability by making systematic and well-reasoned judgments based on relevant data and facts. Effectively identifies potential risks, issues, and improvement opportunities in complex scenarios, and proactively evaluates the impact of proposed solutions to support informed decision-making.


Communication

Communicates ideas clearly and concisely while actively listening to others. Adapts communication style based on verbal and non-verbal cues to ensure alignment and understanding. Effectively conveys information through both verbal and written communication, positively influencing stakeholders toward required actions.


Continual Learning

Shows a strong commitment to continuous learning and professional development. Actively leverages organizational learning opportunities to enhance technical and functional skills. Regularly updates knowledge of new tools, technologies, and processes relevant to the role, and ensures competencies are consistently updated in iEvolve.


Customer Focus

Demonstrates a customer-centric approach by effectively addressing customer requirements while striving to exceed expectations. Collaborates closely with customers to strengthen business relationships and proactively identifies opportunities to add value by understanding evolving market and customer needs.


Drive for Results

Exhibits a strong drive to achieve results with a consistent focus on quality and timely delivery. Maintains disciplined execution of tasks and contributes to a high-performance work culture by following best practices. Effectively utilizes organizational resources and capabilities to achieve desired outcomes.

Presentation Skill

Prepares and delivers well-structured and engaging presentations tailored to diverse audiences. Uses appropriate presentation tools and techniques to clearly explain concepts, share information, and influence decisions or actions effectively.


Values / Conduct

Consistently demonstrates behavior aligned with the organizationâ€™s core values and code of conduct. Makes ethical and responsible decisions while maintaining integrity, accountability, and professionalism, even while working under pressure to achieve results.

